description: Demolition of the existing building and erection of five buildings comprising self-storage space, office space and retail/commercial space, with residential units (Use Class C3) on the upper levels, new landscaping and public realm, ancillary servicing and plant, car and cycle parking, and associated works, subject to Deed of Agreement dated 30th March 2023 under Section 106 of Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
